{"tid":2184826,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本94年歷史主題公園  豐島園謝幕  來園者均表示惋惜","createTime":"2020-09-02T00:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T05:30:29.000Z","uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7e069d9acefab7d578dd133b2bc1f9e817ed68","tid":2184826,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:59:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kV5Lp4DgmFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkV5Lp4DgmFA&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=6747f556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kV5Lp4DgmFA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zj1On2ZyqvA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZj1On2ZyqvA&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=4f9953ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Zj1On2ZyqvA</a><br />\n<br />\n東京都少數的遊樂園「豐島園」在8月31日正式關門94年的歷史謝幕。在惜別之聲中，官方釋放的長達7分鐘的煙花，給許多遊客紛紛前來觀看這個位於東京都練馬區遊樂園的最後一刻。<br />\n<br />\n「豐島園」社長依田龍也表示「El Dorado(旋轉木馬)會永遠的閃耀著！這些年來真的很謝謝大家了。」<br />\n<br />\n遊樂園內最古老的旋轉木馬也在晚上9點的時候熄上燈，正式結束94年的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n來園遊客「我從小的時候就一直在搭旋轉木馬，看到它要消失了真的很捨不得。我的成人式也想在這邊舉辦，結果無法如願。真的非常悲傷」。<br />\n<br />\n1926年開幕的「豐島園」。當時擁有世界首創的室內滑雪場、世界首創的流水游泳池、最先進的大型遊樂設施都依序導入。長年以來紮根在當地，受到各世代的喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n- 來園遊客(80歲)表示：「幼稚園的時候遠足都會來這邊，很希望這裡持續開下去」<br />\n- 來園遊客(30歲)表示：「看到旋轉木馬已經要最後一次了，身為練馬區民真的是非常好的回憶。」<br />\n- 來園遊客：「真的不知道該怎麼表示，但真的很謝謝。」<br />\n<br />\n在不斷的惜別聲中，「豐島園」終於迎來最後一天。<br />\n<br />\n在關門之後，該設施將改變成為公園等，包括展示世界級的電影哈利波特衣裝等等的設施，預計2023年會重新以新的姿態開幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nippon.com/hk/news/fnn2020090179867/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nippon.com%2Fhk%2Fnews%2Ffnn2020090179867%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=769ac0fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nippon.com/hk/news/fnn2020090179867/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/79867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fnn.jp%2Farticles%2F-%2F79867&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYZODbC9uMYpCHTvDpi7yeoo%3D&h=ca5e93ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/79867</a>"},{"pid":"2c704a51c81e51207d83bf7d0e012df7ea8d2c5f","tid":2184826,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"變harry potter studio?"},{"pid":"24c8f24f4d1298dfc6aeeedf7ad220888bb0b0df","tid":2184826,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c704a51c81e51207d83bf7d0e012df7ea8d2c5f","tid":2184826,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"變harry potter studio?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"33fb9c095c67309630534b963d38b19dc3b5aea3","tid":2184826,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24c8f24f4d1298dfc6aeeedf7ad220888bb0b0df","tid":2184826,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c704a51c81e51207d83bf7d0e012df7ea8d2c5f","tid":2184826,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"變harry potter studio?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"咁都好，點都好過變成地產項目。"},{"pid":"9357700be2331554508b7b6a156c49b65e50c1fb","tid":2184826,"uid":194120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33fb9c095c67309630534b963d38b19dc3b5aea3","tid":2184826,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24c8f24f4d1298dfc6aeeedf7ad220888bb0b0df","tid":2184826,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c704a51c81e51207d83bf7d0e012df7ea8d2c5f","tid":2184826,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"變harry potter studio?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:30:09.000Z","msg":"咁都好，點都好過變成地產項目。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:41:07.000Z","msg":"香港荔園啓德都起晒樓"},